## What If I've Already Tried SEO and It Didn't Work?

Most failed SEO attempts stem from three patterns: generic advice applied without understanding your specific market, thin content that ticks keyword boxes without building topical authority, or a scatter-gun approach targeting isolated keywords rather than building interconnected content networks.

Effective SEO for Reading businesses requires local market knowledge, a methodical topical authority strategy, and patience — typically 6–12 months of consistent work before compound growth takes effect.

Previous SEO work that did not deliver almost certainly reflects a methodology problem rather than an SEO problem.

